            <node TEXT="问题：要输出256种不同的灰度，需要将一个区域分成多少个单元？" ID="KxmhaHZMHB" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E8%A6%81%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA256%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%88%86%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%EF%BC%9F%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
          </node>
          <node TEXT="例2：" ID="ayY3dpgdFV" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B2%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork">
            <node TEXT="设显示器为15英寸(指对角线长度)，1280×1024点（12英寸×9英寸），则该显示器的水平分辨率为1280/12 =106.7dpi，垂直分辨率为113.8dpi（dot per inch）。一般的激光打印机的分辨率有：300dpi×300dpi，600dpi×600dpi，720dpi×720dpi等。所以打出来的图象要比计算机显示出来的空间分辨率高。" ID="NTNAs9kada" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%BA15%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8(%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%B9%E8%A7%92%E7%BA%BF%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6)%EF%BC%8C1280%C3%971024%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8812%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8%C3%979%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E8%AF%A5%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%BA1280/12%20=106.7dpi%EF%BC%8C%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%BA113.8dpi%EF%BC%88dot%20per%20inch%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A300dpi%C3%97300dpi%EF%BC%8C600dpi%C3%97600dpi%EF%BC%8C720dpi%C3%97720dpi%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%93%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E8%B1%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%AF%94%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87%E9%AB%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
          </node>
          <node TEXT="例3：" ID="VkCFf2C0ss" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B3%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork">
            <node TEXT="假设有一幅240×180×8bit的灰度图，当用分辨率为300dpi×300dpi的激光打印机将其打印到12.8×9.6英寸的纸上时，是否能将灰度级别完全打印出来？每个象素的图案有多大？" ID="KGvZegXgVf" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%85240%C3%97180%C3%978bit%E7%9A%84%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E7%94%A8%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%BA300dpi%C3%97300dpi%E7%9A%84%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%9C%BA%E5%B0%86%E5%85%B6%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E5%88%B012.8%C3%979.6%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%B8%E4%B8%8A%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%86%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%9F%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E8%B1%A1%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E6%A1%88%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%9F%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
            <node TEXT="解：这张纸最多可以打(300×12.8)×(300×9.6)=3840×2880个点，所以每个象素可以用(3840/240)×(2880/180)=16×16个点大小的图案来表示，即一个象素对应256个点。如果这16×16的方块中一个黑点也没有，就可以表示灰度256；有一个黑点，就表示灰度255；依次类推，当都是黑点时，表示灰度0。这样，16×16的方块可以表示257级灰度，比要求的8bit共256级灰度还多了一个。所以上面的那幅图的灰度级别完全能够打印出来。" ID="O2PGx6jjXV" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%9A%E8%BF%99%E5%BC%A0%E7%BA%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%93(300%C3%9712.8)%C3%97(300%C3%979.6)=3840%C3%972880%E4%B8%AA%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E8%B1%A1%E7%B4%A0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8(3840/240)%C3%97(2880/180)=16%C3%9716%E4%B8%AA%E7%82%B9%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E6%A1%88%E6%9D%A5%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%B1%A1%E7%B4%A0%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94256%E4%B8%AA%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E8%BF%9916%C3%9716%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%9D%97%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%BB%91%E7%82%B9%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6256%EF%BC%9B%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%BB%91%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6255%EF%BC%9B%E4%BE%9D%E6%AC%A1%E7%B1%BB%E6%8E%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%BB%91%E7%82%B9%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A60%E3%80%82%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C16%C3%9716%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%9D%97%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA257%E7%BA%A7%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%94%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%848bit%E5%85%B1256%E7%BA%A7%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%98%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E3%80%82%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%82%A3%E5%B9%85%E5%9B%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
          </node>
        </node>
